
PREREQUISITES

  * quvi 0.2.17+  <http://quvi.googlecode.com/>
  * Perl 5.10.1+  <http://perl.org/>

Additionally (to build):
  * ExtUtils::MakeMaker <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?ExtUtils::MakeMaker>
  * ExtUtils::PkgConfig <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?ExtUtils::PkgConfig>
  * ExtUtils::Depends   <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?ExtUtils::Depends>


INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test (optional, see notes below)
  make install (see notes below)

See Makefile.PL if you need to edit the CXXFLAGS. Refer to the
ExtUtils::MakeMaker documentation for more instructions.

You can define the installation prefix with INSTALL_BASE, e.g.:
  perl Makefile.PL INSTALL_BASE=/usr/local

Recommended reading:
  * <http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?ExtUtils::MakeMaker>
  * <http://perldoc.perl.org/ExtUtils/MakeMaker/FAQ.html>


TESTS

If you run the tests and you want to run the internet based tests,
define HAVE_INTERNET with "make test", e.g.:
  env HAVE_INTERNET=1 make test

